Class Sequence

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2.mwe2impl.Sequence
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeStep, ITransformationStep
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ForEachLoop, ForLoop, Parallel, WhileLoop

    public class Sequence
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITransformationStep, ICompositeStep
    Composite transformation step that implements a basic sequence control flow construction. It initializes and executes its contained steps in the same sequence they have been defined.
